nodes.title: Card
nodes.metaDescription: TenX enables you to spend your Bitcoin and Ether worldwide. With the TenX Visa Card, you can simply pay online and offline anytime, everywhere.
nodes.metaTitle: Crypto Card: Pay everywhere with your Visa Debit Card

childMarkdownRemark.html:
• Freedom to spend bitcoin, ether, and litecoin with the tap of a card
  • Your crypto is converted to cash in a seamless and instant payment

• Pay in local currency wherever you go, no forex fees
  • Withdraw cash from any supported ATM internationally

• Accepted at more than 54 million Visa merchant locations in over 200 countries
  • Pay for online shopping with fraud prevention by Visa’s 3-D Secure

• Automated and instant crypto to cash conversion when you pay
  • No manual conversion needed from you

• Real-time notifications when your card is used
  • Advanced security options to lock and unlock card
  • 2 Factor Authentication for added security

• Track TenX Visa Card purchases and expenses in real-time
  • See detailed transaction history and download monthly reports

• Receive instantly upon approval
  • Spend online anywhere Visa is accepted
  • Full security controls through the app

content.title: FAQs about the TenX Visa Card

faqs.question: How much does the TenX Visa Card cost?

childMarkdownRemark.html: There is a one-time fee that costs EUR 15 for users in the EU/EEA and USD 15 for users in APAC.

faqs.question: How do I order a TenX Visa Card?

childMarkdownRemark.html: You can place your order through the TenX app. A step-by-step guide is available to help you with it.
It typically takes 7 to 9 days for EU/EEA addresses and up to 5 weeks for APAC addresses.

faqs.question: How do I pay using crypto?

childMarkdownRemark.html: Just tap, swipe, or use pin & chip with your TenX Visa Card. We take care of the crypto to fiat conversion for you automatically when you pay at any merchant.
